#include <bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

#define boost ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);cin.tie(0);cout.tie(0)

typedef long long ll;

int main(){
	boost;
	ll T,N,i,j,k;
	vector<ll> vi;
	cin >> T;
	while(T--){
		vi.clear();
		cin >> N ;
		for(i = 0 ; i < N ; i++){
			ll num;
			cin >> num;
			vi.push_back(num);
		}
		sort(vi.begin(),vi.end(),greater<ll>());
		for(i = 0 ; i < N-1 ; i++){
			if(vi[i]==vi[i+1])
				break;
		}
		if(i < N-1)
			cout << "NO" << endl;
		else
			cout << "YES" << endl;
	}
}
